Systemd Flow:

Boot
  ↓
Kernel
  ↓
systemd
  ↓
network.target
  ↓
multi-user.target
  ↓
system_monitor.service (oneshot)
  ↓
ExecStart → system_monitor.sh

7. Conclusion

Linux server monitoring and backup automation fully implemented

Cron and systemd provide reliable automation

SSH and firewall hardening ensures security

Logs and backups are properly retained and accessible
